'''暴蛭'''（{{sn|''Tyrannobdella rex''}}）是2010年在[[秘鲁|秘鲁]]发现的一种[[水蛭|水蛭]]，身长可达约7厘米，上颌具有大型的牙齿，缺少下颌，生殖器十分微小。如同其近亲[[鼻蛭|鼻蛭]]，暴蛭亦可寄生于[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]（包括[[人类|人类]]）的[[黏膜|黏膜]]尤其是[[鼻腔|鼻腔]]黏膜。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=''Tyrannobdella rex'' N. Gen. N. Sp. and the Evolutionary Origins of Mucosal Leech Infestations|author=|url=https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0010057|last=Phillips|first=Anna J.|last2=Arauco-Brown|first2=Renzo|date=2010-04-14|journal=PLOS ONE|issue=4|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0010057|others=|year=|volume=5|page=|pages=e10057|language=en|issn=1932-6203|pmc=PMC2854684|pmid=20418947|last3=Oceguera-Figueroa|first3=Alejandro|last4=Gomez|first4=Gloria P.|last5=Beltrán|first5=María|last6=Lai|first6=Yi-Te|last7=Siddall|first7=Mark E.|access-date=2020-10-12|archive-date=2020-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505002809/https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0010057|dead-url=no}}</ref>

